Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{S-Since when were you... [9 frames]}Em ở đó bao lâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{Water sploosh...}Nước bắn tung tóe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{You know this?}Em biết đó là gì à?
