Comment: 1,0:02:45.71,0:02:48.63,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,TẬP 24\NNHỮNG CÔ GÁI KHÔNG MAY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey Spike, where the hell are we?!}Này, Spike, ta đang ở chỗ quái nào thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.72,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Isn't it Earth?}Ta ở Trái Đất.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:07.75,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Earth?!}Trái Đất ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, this ship was headed for Mars!}Lẽ ra chúng ta phải đến Sao Hỏa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{Why the hell are we on Earth\Nall of a sudden?!}Sao đột nhiên lại ở Trái Đất?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:13.50,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Dunno. [extra lead-in]}Tôi chịu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.19,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Shit, this isn't funny.}Chết tiệt, đùa tôi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{While we're wasting time, our fugitive...!}Trong khi ta lãng phí thời gian,\Nkẻ đào tẩu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{It was the first big one in a while.}Lâu rồi mới theo dấu\Nmột tên được treo thưởng cao thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{In any case, why the hell are we on—?}Vậy thế quái nào mà ta lại—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{Jet.}Jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{The women are gone. [9 frames]}Cánh phụ nữ đi mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:36.65,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Listen, if you lead me to that "water sploosh"\Nplace, I'll give you something good.}{\i0}Nghe này, nếu em dẫn chị đến chỗ "nước bắn tung tóe",\Nchị sẽ cho em thứ này hay lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Good thing? What?}{\i0}{\i1}Thứ hay ư? Là thứ gì?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{Something very, tremendously,\Nwonderfully good.}Một thứ cực kỳ hay ho,\Nsiêu đẳng, tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:48.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{Something very, tremendously,\Nwonderfully good!}Một thứ cực kỳ hay ho,\Nsiêu đẳng, tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hot!}Nóng quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!}Nóng quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{This!}Chỗ này!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{Water sploosh!}Nước bắn tung tóe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{I knew I shouldn't have trusted you...}Chị nghĩ là lỗi của chị\Nkhi trông cậy ở em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, I found Ed!}Tìm thấy Ed rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ed has been found?}Ed được tìm thấy rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{What, you know them?}Gì cơ? Tụi nó là bạn của em ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:11.50,Default - Alt,split,0,0,0,,{35 point 38 point 0, 35 point\N48 point 1, 35 point 48 point 2...}35. 48.5...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:09.99,Main,split,0,0,0,,{This!}Đây nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.49,Main,split,0,0,0,,{This, this, this!}Đây nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.35,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hey, can I have your nails?}Này, đưa móng tay của chị cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.25,Main,split,0,0,0,,{N-Nails? [added the hesitation]}Móng tay ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.61,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I'm collecting them!}Em sưu tập chúng!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:16.50,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Can I, please?}Làm ơn nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.00,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Just the pinky one will do!}Ngón út là được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:24.01,Default - Alt,split,0,0,0,,{35 point 52 point 3, 35 point...}35.52.3, 35...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.35,Main,split,0,0,0,,{This, this!}Đây nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:22.78,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Come on... can I have it? Please?}Cho em nhé? Em xin chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.78,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What are you guys?!}Các em là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.01,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Mấy đứa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ed?!}Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:40.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{Is that really you... Ed?}Có thật là con không? Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry about that.}Tôi xin lỗi về việc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's the best way\Nto make the kids listen.}Đó là cách tốt nhất\Nkhiến bọn trẻ lắng nghe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's all right.}Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Is Ed from this place?}Ed đến từ đây à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{She wandered in about five years ago. [9 frames]}Ed lang thang ở khu này\Nkhoảng năm năm trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{Before I knew it, she was eating with us\Nas if it had always been that way.}Trước khi tôi nhận ra, chúng tôi đã\Nngồi ăn cùng nhau như thể đó giờ vẫn vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{And about three years ago,\Nshe wandered away.}Sau đó, khoảng ba năm trước,\NEd lại đi lang thang,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{As if she was a cat or something.}như một con mèo hay thứ gì kiểu thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{I was wondering how she\Nwas doing nowadays,}Tôi đã tự hỏi đứa trẻ ở đâu,\Ncó an toàn không.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:25.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{but I didn't think she\Nwould suddenly appear.}Tôi không ngờ nó lại đột ngột trở về.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{All right, it's time to eat!}Được rồi, đến giờ ăn rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{Dear Lord up in the heavens...}Lạy Cha chúng con ở trên trời...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{Never mind the rest. Let's eat!}Các con biết đoạn sau là gì rồi. Ăn thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{Let's eat!}Ăn thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{I have to get going now...}Giờ tôi phải đi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:54.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{What, you can stay longer, right?}Gì cơ? Sao phải vội vàng thế chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:55.74,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I'm actually looking for something...}Thực ra tôi đang tìm một thứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.48,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Ed knows where it is.}Ed biết nó ở đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{We just came here for food.}Ta chỉ đến đây để ăn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{You...}Em thật là...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{You have to gimme something good!}Nhớ phải cho em thứ hay ho đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, Ed.}Dì xém quên đó Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{There's something good in\Nthe desk drawer over there.}Ngăn kéo bàn kia có một thứ rất hay ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.65,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Something good?}Thứ hay ho ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.84,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Go get it.}Qua lấy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{Something good!}Thứ hay ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{Inside that drawer.}Nó ở trong ngăn kéo đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Not that.}Không phải cái đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, that. Open it!}Ừ, đúng đó. Mở ra đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.10,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Her father.}Là bố của con đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.16,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Whose?}Gì cơ? Của ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{He came looking for Ed about 2 months ago.}Khoảng hai tháng trước,\Nông ấy đến đây tìm Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{He said he forgot that he\Nhad put her in an orphanage}Ông ấy nói ông ấy quên mất rằng\Nđã gửi Ed ở trại mồ côi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{and that he had been looking for\N7 years, hopping around the world.}Suốt bảy năm\Nông ấy đã đi tìm đứa nhỏ khắp thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{I hope she will be able to meet him...}Tôi hy vọng họ có thể đoàn tụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{People have to cherish what ties they have...}Người ta phải trân trọng\Nmối quan hệ máu mủ ruột rà.
Comment: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,ĐÃ CẬP NHẬT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{Are you... Faye?}Cậu là Faye à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{Impossible...}Không thể nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{Really?}Là cậu thật ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's me, Sally Yung!}Là tớ đây, Sally Yung!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{I was in your high school\Ngraduating class!}Chúng ta cùng học chung cấp ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}Không sao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{I was really surprised.}Tớ sốc quá thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{I thought you were a ghost.\NYou look just like back then...}Tớ cứ tưởng cậu là ma.\NCậu trông y hệt hồi xưa.
